<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>据悉，攀大高速（四川境）</span></span><span><span>总里程短、桥隧比高、单位里程造价高</span></span><span><span>。</span></span><span><span>项目</span></span><span><span>总里程41.002公里，</span></span><span><span>而</span></span><span><span>桥隧总长</span></span><span><span>就有</span></span><span><span>33.183公里，桥隧比高达81%，</span></span><span><span>一般高速公路每公里造价约0.86亿元，但是攀大高速公路</span></span><span><span>每公里造价</span></span><span><span>高达</span></span><span><span>1.63亿元。</span></span><span><span>攀大高速（四川境）沿线</span></span><span><span>地质</span></span><span><span>结构</span></span><span><span>复杂，在施工过程中面临瓦斯突出、高瓦斯、低瓦斯、断层、岩爆、涌水、采空、</span></span><span><span>高边坡开挖、</span></span><span><span>高空作业等诸多困难和风险，施工难度</span></span><span><span>极</span></span><span><span>大。</span></span><span><span>其中，</span></span><span><span>宝鼎2号隧道</span></span><span><span>是攀大高速项目的关键控制性工程，</span></span><span><span>全长8.775公里，</span></span><span><span>是</span></span><span><span>全国在建高速公路最长的瓦斯突出隧道</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>其</span></span><span><span>施工难度和安全风险均位居国内同类型隧道前列。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
